          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audiobook 9781441714244" href="/book/show/7062680-angle-of-repose">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41918078-debbie?shelf=classics">classics</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41918078-debbie?shelf=2021-reads">2021-reads</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41918078-debbie?shelf=audiobook">audiobook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/41918078-debbie?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>, 
